{"tid":758374,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"晚。（想加入Happy YanYi Family 就報名啦）","createTime":"2018-07-27T15:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T12:23:32.000Z","uid":71166,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b056cb0537914ae0bc7dbdd5ccef6185fe37378c","tid":758374,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T15:35:51.000Z","msg":"今日同大家食任食火鍋<br />\n人頭138元<br />\n26款湯底任揀<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/231125_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F231125_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0a04fbba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋揀咗烤魚（有鯇魚周田魚選擇）<br />\n我哋揀嘅係鯇魚 <br />\n嘩好大嚿魚呀<br />\n魚質鮮嫰唔鞋又唔腥<br />\n炸到面頭脆扑扑好惹味<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/231315_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F231315_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bc189d3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/231307_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F231307_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=167f3ed2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/232140_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F232140_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=faa07b5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n飲品有十幾款選擇<br />\n連可樂，燕京都有<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/231600_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F231600_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=63a7ec20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/231728_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F231728_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=90ce894a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n識飲一定係飲蒸餾水<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/231724_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F231724_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ab0a5b40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n火鍋食物自助形式，款式十分多選擇<br />\n全部都好新鮮，食物又refill得好快<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/232401_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F232401_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7befd9d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/232409_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F232409_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=569745dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/232348_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F232348_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=59ff0aa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/232341_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F232341_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9c90060a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/232332_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F232332_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ae9723a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/232324_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F232324_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=124cce4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/232317_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F232317_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c93ef29a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/232541_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F232541_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d5893651&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/232552_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F232552_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=97f9051d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完烤魚就可以開始打邊爐<br />\n粉絲同韮菜索埋啲湯真係好鮮甜超入味<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/232901_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F232901_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=aece4f9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/232909_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F232909_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=83b6d390&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全部都好好味<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/233155_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F233155_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8f1a1976&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想第一手知道欣宜去咗邊度食嘢快啲追蹤我啦，<br />\n想同埋我哋一齊搵好嘢食，快啲加入Happy YanYi Family啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"493b7f53747cf7a2781a80648ea078c8bd35b002","tid":758374,"uid":165024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T15:36:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0525384003f58ecf8aa70e49ea779193f287cd","tid":758374,"uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"493b7f53747cf7a2781a80648ea078c8bd35b002","tid":758374,"uid":165024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T15:36:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T15:37:39.000Z","msg":"cc加唔加入Happy YanYi Family <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e78ec29dfe3b58eaff78555d4d1d572cbbb76d2","tid":758374,"uid":152262,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T15:42:02.000Z","msg":"Join! Vip member ok?"},{"pid":"bd6ef57f90492a65c99231d265119717257eb17a","tid":758374,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0a0525384003f58ecf8aa70e49ea779193f287cd","tid":758374,"uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"493b7f53747cf7a2781a80648ea078c8bd35b002","tid":758374,"uid":165024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T15:36:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T15:37:39.000Z","msg":"cc加唔加入Happy YanYi Family <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyT